Interesting, **Sonic Paradox** is 3D now. You can watch it on [Newgrounds](https://www.newgrounds.com/portal/view/1038591) or [Youtube](https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=nOUksum3ETA).

This part in particular was funny since [characters just pop-up](https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=nOUksum3ETA&t=540s) in Sobic-related media.
